INSTALL file for VLMC

For now we don't use autotools to build the project.
If you have any experiences with autotools and want to help, please contact us
on <vlmc-devel@vlmc.org>.

Dependencies
============

- Latest version of VLC installed (from the git repository)
- Qt framework >= 4.5.0

Get the sources
===============

	git clone git://github.com/VLMC/vlmc.git

Building VLMC
=============

A typical way to build VLMC is:

	qmake
	make

Running VLMC
============

	./vlmc

Issues
======

If you run into problems, you can ask for help on <vlmc-devel@vlmc.org> and
IRC channel #vlmc on Freenode.

